## Common Validators

- `v.id("tableName")` - Document ID
- `v.null()` - Null value (not undefined)
- `v.int64()` - BigInt (not v.bigint())
- `v.record(v.string(), v.any())` - Record type
- `v.union(...)` - Union types
- `v.literal("value")` - Literal values

